'placement [in the parallel context of PY Qa] suggests a title of the religious sphere [...] However the ''title'' (ri)-ma is a hapax which is difficult to interpret. So we are dealing perhaps with another instance of a noun in -mar martos like du-ma or da-ma for which only δάμαρ is attested in the Greek lexicon.
